## University

Institutions o f   learning and  research are the  purview of the University Influence. Access to  the  halls  of learning  can  help  you with  any  number of resources,  from  ancient

languages to research assistance  to many impressionable  young minds. School boards, students from kindergarten through college, graduate students, professors, teachers, deans, Greek orders and a variety of staff fill the ivy-covered halls.

