## &amp;pip

Each Epiphling embodies a concept, such as Peace, Envy, Speed or Death. Garou don't really understand how Epiphlings fit into the spiritual hierarchy, and theories abound among scholars o f  Umbral affairs. Epiphlings often  manifest as Gafflings, and Storytellers can use Gaffling Traits for Epiphlings encountered  in play.

